      "name": "Nebulous, Dragon Ruler of Shadows",
      "effect": "You can discard this card and 1 DARK or Dragon monster, then target 2 of your banished \"Dragon Ruler\" monsters with different Attributes, except \"Nebulous, Dragon Ruler of Shadows\"; Special Summon them, but they cannot attack this turn. You can banish this card and 1 DARK or Dragon monster from your GY, then target 1 \"Eclepsis, Dragon Ruler of Woes\" in your GY; Special Summon it. You can only use 1 \"Nebulous, Dragon Ruler of Shadows\" effect per turn, and only once that turn.",
      "official": false
    },
